LA CAÑADA FLINTRIDGE MEETINGS AGENDAS/MINUTES/VIDEO

Welcome to City's Agendas/Minutes/City Council Video page where you can access the upcoming agenda packet, live video stream of City Council Meetings, as well as archived videos(City Council meetings only), agendas and minutes. City Council and Commission meetings are held in the City Council Chambers at La Cañada Flintridge City Hall, One Civic Center Drive, La Cañada Flintridge.

Meetings are arranged by date with most recent at the top of the list. For City Council on demand videos, click Video to watch the meeting. You may also view meeting Agenda /Minutes by clicking the respective link. You can also search the archives by typing keywords into the search box.

Live and Archived video can be viewed on most desktop browsers and a range of popular mobile devices. For additional information on supported platforms, please view the minimum system requirements.



Hold "Ctrl" on the keyboard then click the link below to open the link in a new tab:
